  "body": "erigon does not respect the `input` field for the json-rpc-method `eth_call`, it only accepts `data`. \r\n\r\nsee: https://ethereum.github.io/execution-apis/api-documentation\r\n\r\n#### System information\r\n\r\nErigon version: `v2.48.1`\r\n\r\nOS & Version: Linux\r\n\r\nChain/Network: ethereum mainnet\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\n\r\n```\r\n$ curl -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":2,\"method\":\"eth_call\",\"params\":[{\"from\":\"0x0000000000000000000000000000000000000000\",\"input\":\"0xfeaf968c\",\"to\":\"0x5f4ec3df9cbd43714fe2740f5e3616155c5b8419\"},\"latest\"]}' http://erigon:8545\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":2,\"result\":\"\"}\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\n\r\n```\r\n$ curl -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":2,\"method\":\"eth_call\",\"params\":[{\"from\":\"0x0000000000000000000000000000000000000000\",\"input\":\"0xfeaf968c\",\"to\":\"0x5f4ec3df9cbd43714fe2740f5e3616155c5b8419\"},\"latest\"]}' http://erigon.in:8545\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":2,\"error\":{\"code\":-32000,\"message\":\"execution reverted\"}}\r\n```\r\n\r\nnote: this is working:\r\n```\r\n$ curl -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":2,\"method\":\"eth_call\",\"params\":[{\"from\":\"0x0000000000000000000000000000000000000000\",\"data\":\"0xfeaf968c\",\"to\":\"0x5f4ec3df9cbd43714fe2740f5e3616155c5b8419\"},\"latest\"]}' http://erigon:8545\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":2,\"result\":\"\"}\r\n```\r\n",
